6556 bool PlayerbotAI::ApplyActiveTalentSpec()
6557 {
6558  // empty talent spec -> nothing to apply -> fully applied
6559  if (m_activeTalentSpec.specClass == 0 || m_activeTalentSpec.specPurpose == TSP_NONE)
6560  return true;
6561 
6562  // Some basic error checking just in case
6563  if (m_activeTalentSpec.specClass != m_bot->getClass())
6564  return false;
6565 
6566  std::vector<uint16> talentsToLearn;
6567  talentsToLearn.reserve(71);
6568  for (int i = 0; i < 71; i++)
6569  {
6570  if (m_activeTalentSpec.talentId[i] != 0)
6571  talentsToLearn.push_back(m_activeTalentSpec.talentId[i]);
6572  }
6573 
6574  PlayerTalentMap ptm = m_bot->GetTalents(m_bot->GetActiveSpec());
6575  // First do a check as to whether all known talents are in the talent spec
6576  for (PlayerTalentMap::iterator iter = ptm.begin(); iter != ptm.end(); iter++)
6577  {
6578  PlayerTalent talent = (*iter).second;
6579 
6580  // WARNING: There may be more than 71 'talents' in the PTM - unlearned talents are simply set as disabled - not removed
6581  if (talent.state == PLAYERSPELL_REMOVED)
6582  continue;
6583 
6584  // currentRank = 0 to (MAX_RANK-1) not 1 to MAX_RANK
6585  for (int i = 0; i <= (int) talent.currentRank; i++)
6586  {
6587  int j = 0; // why 0 and not -1? Because if talentsToCheck (no TalentSpec) is empty and talents have been learned -> NOK
6588  for (std::vector<uint16>::iterator it = talentsToLearn.begin(); it != talentsToLearn.end(); it++)
6589  {
6590  if (talentsToLearn.at(j) == talent.talentEntry->TalentID)
6591  {
6592  talentsToLearn.erase(it);
6593  j = -1; // So j = -1 -> learned talent found in talentspec
6594  break;
6595  }
6596  j++;
6597  }
6598 
6599  // j == -1 signifies talent has been found in talent spec
6600  if (-1 != j)
6601  {
6602  TellMaster("I've learned talents that are not in my talent spec. If you want me to learn the talent spec anyway you should have me reset my talents.");
6603  return false;
6604  }
6605  }
6606  }
6607 
6608  int x = 0;
6609  for (std::vector<uint16>::iterator iter = talentsToLearn.begin(); iter != talentsToLearn.end(); iter++)
6610  {
6611  // find current talent rank
6612  uint32 learnTalentRank = 0;
6613  if (PlayerTalent const* talent = m_bot->GetKnownTalentById(talentsToLearn.at(x)))
6614  learnTalentRank = talent->currentRank + 1;
6615  // else -> not known -> to learn = 0
6616 
6617  // check if we have enough talent points
6618  uint32 freeTalentPointsBefore = m_bot->GetFreeTalentPoints();
6619  if (0 == freeTalentPointsBefore)
6620  return true;
6621 
6622  m_bot->LearnTalent(talentsToLearn.at(x), learnTalentRank);
6623  if (freeTalentPointsBefore == m_bot->GetFreeTalentPoints())
6624  {
6625  // Do not tell master - error is logged server side, master gets generic failure warning from calling function.
6626  //TellMaster("Failed to learn talent - Class: %i; TalentId: %i; TalentRank: %i. This error has been logged.", m_bot->getClass(), talentsToLearn.at(x), learnTalentRank);
6627  DEBUG_LOG("[PlayerbotAI]: ApplyActiveTalentSpec failure - Class: %i; TalentId: %i; TalentRank: %i.", m_bot->getClass(), talentsToLearn.at(x), learnTalentRank);
6628  return false;
6629  }
6630 
6631  x++;
6632  }
6633 
6634  return true;
6635 }

6891 
6892 void PlayerbotAI::extractQuestIds(const std::string& text, std::list<uint32>& questIds) const
6893 {
6894  uint8 pos = 0;
6895  while (true)
6896  {
6897  int i = text.find("Hquest:", pos);
6898  if (i == -1)
6899  break;
6900  pos = i + 7;
6901  int endPos = text.find(':', pos);
6902  if (endPos == -1)
6903  break;
6904  std::string idC = text.substr(pos, endPos - pos);
6905  uint32 id = atol(idC.c_str());
6906  pos = endPos;
6907  if (id)
6908  questIds.push_back(id);
6909  }
6910 }
6911 
6912 // Build an hlink for Quests in Yellow
6913 void PlayerbotAI::MakeQuestLink(Quest const* quest, std::ostringstream& out)
6914 {
6915  std::string questTitle = quest->GetTitle();
6916  QuestLocalization(questTitle, quest->GetQuestId());
6917  out << "|cFFEFFD00|Hquest:" << quest->GetQuestId() << ':' << quest->GetQuestLevel() << "|h[" << questTitle << "]|h|r";
6918 }
6919 
6920 // Build an hlink for Weapon skills in Aqua
6921 void PlayerbotAI::MakeWeaponSkillLink(const SpellEntry* sInfo, std::ostringstream& out, uint32 skillid)
6922 {
6923  int loc = GetMaster()->GetSession()->GetSessionDbcLocale();
6924  out << "|cff00ffff|Hspell:" << sInfo->Id << "|h[" << sInfo->SpellName[loc] << " : " << m_bot->GetSkillValue(skillid) << " /" << m_bot->GetSkillMax(skillid) << "]|h|r";
6925 }

6927 // Build an hlink for spells in White

6940 // Builds a hlink for an item, but since its
6941 // only a ItemPrototype, we cant fill in everything
6942 void PlayerbotAI::MakeItemLink(const ItemPrototype* item, std::ostringstream& out)
6943 {
6944  // Color
6945  out << "|c";
6946  switch (item->Quality)
6947  {
6948  case ITEM_QUALITY_POOR: out << "ff9d9d9d"; break; //GREY
6949  case ITEM_QUALITY_NORMAL: out << "ffffffff"; break; //WHITE
6950  case ITEM_QUALITY_UNCOMMON: out << "ff1eff00"; break; //GREEN
6951  case ITEM_QUALITY_RARE: out << "ff0070dd"; break; //BLUE
6952  case ITEM_QUALITY_EPIC: out << "ffa335ee"; break; //PURPLE
6953  case ITEM_QUALITY_LEGENDARY: out << "ffff8000"; break; //ORANGE
6954  case ITEM_QUALITY_ARTIFACT: out << "ffe6cc80"; break; //LIGHT YELLOW
6955  case ITEM_QUALITY_HEIRLOOM: out << "ffe6cc80"; break; //LIGHT YELLOW
6956  default: out << "ffff0000"; break; //Don't know color, so red?
6957  }
6958  out << "|Hitem:";
6959 
6960  // Item Id
6961  out << item->ItemId << ":";
6962 
6963  // Permanent enchantment, gems, 4 unknowns, and reporter_level
6964  // ->new items wont have enchantments or gems so..
6965  out << "0:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:0";
6966 
6967  // Name
6968  std::string name = item->Name1;
6969  ItemLocalization(name, item->ItemId);
6970  out << "|h[" << name << "]|h|r";
6971 
6972  // Stacked items
6973  if (item->BuyCount > 1)
6974  out << "|cff009900x" << item->BuyCount << ".|r";
6975  else
6976  out << "|cff009900.|r";
6977 }
6978 
6979 // Builds a hlink for an item, includes everything
6980 // |color|Hitem:item_id:perm_ench_id:gem1:gem2:gem3:0:0:0:0:reporter_level|h[name]|h|r
6981 void PlayerbotAI::MakeItemLink(const Item* item, std::ostringstream& out, bool IncludeQuantity /*= true*/)
6982 {
6983  const ItemPrototype* proto = item->GetProto();
6984  // Color
6985  out << "|c";
6986  switch (proto->Quality)
6987  {
6988  case ITEM_QUALITY_POOR: out << "ff9d9d9d"; break; //GREY
6989  case ITEM_QUALITY_NORMAL: out << "ffffffff"; break; //WHITE
6990  case ITEM_QUALITY_UNCOMMON: out << "ff1eff00"; break; //GREEN
6991  case ITEM_QUALITY_RARE: out << "ff0070dd"; break; //BLUE
6992  case ITEM_QUALITY_EPIC: out << "ffa335ee"; break; //PURPLE
6993  case ITEM_QUALITY_LEGENDARY: out << "ffff8000"; break; //ORANGE
6994  case ITEM_QUALITY_ARTIFACT: out << "ffe6cc80"; break; //LIGHT YELLOW
6995  case ITEM_QUALITY_HEIRLOOM: out << "ffe6cc80"; break; //LIGHT YELLOW
6996  default: out << "ffff0000"; break; //Don't know color, so red?
6997  }
6998  out << "|Hitem:";
6999 
7000  // Item Id
7001  out << proto->ItemId << ":";
7002 
7003  // Permanent enchantment
7004  out << item->GetEnchantmentId(PERM_ENCHANTMENT_SLOT) << ":";
7005 
7006  // Gems
7007  uint32 g1 = 0, g2 = 0, g3 = 0;
7008  for (uint32 slot = SOCK_ENCHANTMENT_SLOT; slot < SOCK_ENCHANTMENT_SLOT + MAX_GEM_SOCKETS; ++slot)
7009  {
7010  uint32 eId = item->GetEnchantmentId(EnchantmentSlot(slot));
7011  if (!eId) continue;
7012 
7013  SpellItemEnchantmentEntry const* entry = sSpellItemEnchantmentStore.LookupEntry(eId);
7014  if (!entry) continue;
7015 
7016  switch (slot - SOCK_ENCHANTMENT_SLOT)
7017  {
7018  case 1: g1 = entry->GemID; break;
7019  case 2: g2 = entry->GemID; break;
7020  case 3: g3 = entry->GemID; break;
7021  }
7022  }
7023  out << g1 << ":" << g2 << ":" << g3 << ":";
7024 
7025  // Temp enchantment, Bonus Enchantment, Prismatic Enchantment?
7026  // Other stuff, don't know what it is
7027  out << "0:0:0:0:";
7028 
7029  // Reporter Level
7030  out << "0";
7031 
7032  // Name
7033  std::string name = proto->Name1;
7034  ItemLocalization(name, proto->ItemId);
7035  out << "|h[" << name << "]|h|r";
7036 
7037  // Stacked items
7038  if (item->GetCount() > 1 && IncludeQuantity)
7039  out << "x" << item->GetCount() << ' ';
7040 }

7071 void PlayerbotAI::extractAuctionIds(const std::string& text, std::list<uint32>& auctionIds) const
7072 {
7073  uint8 pos = 0;
7074  while (true)
7075  {
7076  int i = text.find("Htitle:", pos);
7077  if (i == -1)
7078  break;
7079  pos = i + 7;
7080  int endPos = text.find('|', pos);
7081  if (endPos == -1)
7082  break;
7083  std::string idC = text.substr(pos, endPos - pos);
7084  uint32 id = atol(idC.c_str());
7085  pos = endPos;
7086  if (id)
7087  auctionIds.push_back(id);
7088  }
7089 }

7091 void PlayerbotAI::extractSpellId(const std::string& text, uint32& spellId) const
7092 {
7093 
7094  // Link format
7095  // |cffffffff|Hspell:" << spellId << ":" << "|h[" << pSpellInfo->SpellName[loc] << "]|h|r";
7096  // cast |cff71d5ff|Hspell:686|h[Shadow Bolt]|h|r";
7097  // 012345678901234567890123456
7098  // base = 16 >| +7 >|
7099 
7100  uint8 pos = 0;
7101 
7102  int i = text.find("Hspell:", pos);
7103  if (i == -1)
7104  return;
7105 
7106  // DEBUG_LOG("[PlayerbotAI]: extractSpellId - first pos %u i %u",pos,i);
7107  pos = i + 7; // start of window in text 16 + 7 = 23
7108  int endPos = text.find('|', pos);
7109  if (endPos == -1)
7110  return;
7111 
7112  // DEBUG_LOG("[PlayerbotAI]: extractSpellId - second endpos : %u pos : %u",endPos,pos);
7113  std::string idC = text.substr(pos, endPos - pos); // 26 - 23
7114  spellId = atol(idC.c_str());
7115  pos = endPos; // end
7116 }

7150 void PlayerbotAI::extractTalentIds(const std::string& text, std::list<talentPair>& talentIds) const
7151 {
7152  // Link format:
7153  // |color|Htalent:talent_id:rank|h[name]|h|r
7154  // |cff4e96f7|Htalent:1396:4|h[Unleashed Fury]|h|r
7155 
7156  uint8 pos = 0;
7157  while (true)
7158  {
7159  int i = text.find("Htalent:", pos);
7160  if (i == -1)
7161  break;
7162  pos = i + 8;
7163  // DEBUG_LOG("extractTalentIds first pos %u i %u",pos,i);
7164  // extract talent_id
7165  int endPos = text.find(':', pos);
7166  if (endPos == -1)
7167  break;
7168  // DEBUG_LOG("extractTalentId second endpos : %u pos : %u",endPos,pos);
7169  std::string idC = text.substr(pos, endPos - pos);
7170  uint32 id = atol(idC.c_str());
7171  pos = endPos + 1;
7172  // extract rank
7173  endPos = text.find('|', pos);
7174  if (endPos == -1)
7175  break;
7176  // DEBUG_LOG("extractTalentId third endpos : %u pos : %u",endPos,pos);
7177  std::string rankC = text.substr(pos, endPos - pos);
7178  uint32 rank = atol(rankC.c_str());
7179  pos = endPos + 1;
7180 
7181  // DEBUG_LOG("extractTalentId second id : %u rank : %u",id,rank);
7182 
7183  if (id)
7184  talentIds.push_back(std::pair<uint32, uint32>(id, rank));
7185  }
7186 }
7187 
7188 void PlayerbotAI::extractGOinfo(const std::string& text, BotObjectList& m_lootTargets) const
7189 {
7190 
7191  // Link format
7192  // |cFFFFFF00|Hfound:" << guid << ':' << entry << ':' << "|h[" << gInfo->name << "]|h|r";
7193  // |cFFFFFF00|Hfound:9582:1731|h[Copper Vein]|h|r
7194 
7195  uint8 pos = 0;
7196  while (true)
7197  {
7198  // extract GO guid
7199  int i = text.find("Hfound:", pos); // base H = 11
7200  if (i == -1) // break if error
7201  break;
7202 
7203  pos = i + 7; //start of window in text 11 + 7 = 18
7204  int endPos = text.find(':', pos); // end of window in text 22
7205  if (endPos == -1) //break if error
7206  break;
7207  std::string guidC = text.substr(pos, endPos - pos); // get string within window i.e guid 22 - 18 = 4
7208  uint32 guid = atol(guidC.c_str()); // convert ascii to long int
7209 
7210  // extract GO entry
7211  pos = endPos + 1;
7212  endPos = text.find(':', pos); // end of window in text
7213  if (endPos == -1) //break if error
7214  break;
7215 
7216  std::string entryC = text.substr(pos, endPos - pos); // get string within window i.e entry
7217  uint32 entry = atol(entryC.c_str()); // convert ascii to float
7218 
7219  ObjectGuid lootCurrent = ObjectGuid(HIGHGUID_GAMEOBJECT, entry, guid);
7220 
7221  if (GameObject* gob = m_bot->GetMap()->GetGameObject(lootCurrent))
7222  m_lootTargets.push_back(gob->GetObjectGuid());
7223  }
7224 }
7225 
7226 // extracts currency in #g#s#c format
7227 uint32 PlayerbotAI::extractMoney(const std::string& text) const
7228 {
7229  // if user specified money in ##g##s##c format
7230  std::string acum = "";
7231  uint32 copper = 0;
7232  for (uint8 i = 0; i < text.length(); i++)
7233  {
7234  if (text[i] == 'g')
7235  {
7236  copper += (atol(acum.c_str()) * 100 * 100);
7237  acum = "";
7238  }
7239  else if (text[i] == 'c')
7240  {
7241  copper += atol(acum.c_str());
7242  acum = "";
7243  }
7244  else if (text[i] == 's')
7245  {
7246  copper += (atol(acum.c_str()) * 100);
7247  acum = "";
7248  }
7249  else if (text[i] == ' ')
7250  break;
7251  else if (text[i] >= 48 && text[i] <= 57)
7252  acum += text[i];
7253  else
7254  {
7255  copper = 0;
7256  break;
7257  }
7258  }
7259  return copper;
7260 }

7262 // finds items in equipment and adds Item* to foundItemList
7263 // also removes found item IDs from itemIdSearchList when found
7264 void PlayerbotAI::findItemsInEquip(std::list<uint32>& itemIdSearchList, std::list<Item*>& foundItemList) const
7265 {
7266  for (uint8 slot = EQUIPMENT_SLOT_START; itemIdSearchList.size() > 0 && slot < EQUIPMENT_SLOT_END; slot++)
7267  {
7268  Item* const pItem = m_bot->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, slot);
7269  if (!pItem)
7270  continue;
7271 
7272  for (std::list<uint32>::iterator it = itemIdSearchList.begin(); it != itemIdSearchList.end(); ++it)
7273  {
7274  if (pItem->GetProto()->ItemId != *it)
7275  continue;
7276 
7277  foundItemList.push_back(pItem);
7278  itemIdSearchList.erase(it);
7279  break;
7280  }
7281  }
7282 }

7284 // finds items in inventory and adds Item* to foundItemList
7285 // also removes found item IDs from itemIdSearchList when found
7286 void PlayerbotAI::findItemsInInv(std::list<uint32>& itemIdSearchList, std::list<Item*>& foundItemList) const
7287 {
7288 
7289  // look for items in main bag
7290  for (uint8 slot = INVENTORY_SLOT_ITEM_START; itemIdSearchList.size() > 0 && slot < INVENTORY_SLOT_ITEM_END; ++slot)
7291  {
7292  Item* const pItem = m_bot->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, slot);
7293  if (!pItem)
7294  continue;
7295 
7296  for (std::list<uint32>::iterator it = itemIdSearchList.begin(); it != itemIdSearchList.end(); ++it)
7297  {
7298  if (pItem->GetProto()->ItemId != *it)
7299  continue;
7300 
7301  if (m_bot->GetTrader() && m_bot->GetTradeData()->HasItem(pItem->GetObjectGuid()))
7302  continue;
7303 
7304  foundItemList.push_back(pItem);
7305  itemIdSearchList.erase(it);
7306  break;
7307  }
7308  }
7309 
7310  // for all for items in other bags
7311  for (uint8 bag = INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_START; itemIdSearchList.size() > 0 && bag < INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_END; ++bag)
7312  {
7313  Bag* const pBag = (Bag*) m_bot->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, bag);
7314  if (!pBag)
7315  continue;
7316 
7317  for (uint8 slot = 0; itemIdSearchList.size() > 0 && slot < pBag->GetBagSize(); ++slot)
7318  {
7319  Item* const pItem = m_bot->GetItemByPos(bag, slot);
7320  if (!pItem)
7321  continue;
7322 
7323  for (std::list<uint32>::iterator it = itemIdSearchList.begin(); it != itemIdSearchList.end(); ++it)
7324  {
7325  if (pItem->GetProto()->ItemId != *it)
7326  continue;
7327 
7328  if (m_bot->GetTrader() && m_bot->GetTradeData()->HasItem(pItem->GetObjectGuid()))
7329  continue;
7330 
7331  foundItemList.push_back(pItem);
7332  itemIdSearchList.erase(it);
7333  break;
7334  }
7335  }
7336  }
7337 }
7338 
7339 void PlayerbotAI::findNearbyGO()
7340 {
7341  if (m_collectObjects.empty())
7342  return;
7343 
7344  GameObjectList tempTargetGOList;
7345 
7346  for (BotEntryList::iterator itr = m_collectObjects.begin(); itr != m_collectObjects.end(); itr++)
7347  {
7348  uint32 entry = *(itr);
7349  GameObjectInfo const* gInfo = ObjectMgr::GetGameObjectInfo(entry);
7350  bool questGO = false;
7351  uint8 needCount = 0;
7352 
7353  for (uint32 i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
7354  {
7355  if (gInfo->questItems[i] != 0) // check whether the gameobject contains quest items
7356  {
7357  questGO = true;
7358  if (IsInQuestItemList(gInfo->questItems[i])) // quest item needed
7359  needCount++;
7360  }
7361  }
7362 
7363  if (questGO && needCount == 0)
7364  {
7365  m_collectObjects.remove(entry); // remove gameobject from collect list
7366  return;
7367  }
7368 
7369  // search for GOs with entry, within range of m_bot
7370  MaNGOS::GameObjectEntryInPosRangeCheck go_check(*m_bot, entry, m_bot->GetPositionX(), m_bot->GetPositionY(), m_bot->GetPositionZ(), float(m_collectDist));
7371  MaNGOS::GameObjectListSearcher<MaNGOS::GameObjectEntryInPosRangeCheck> checker(tempTargetGOList, go_check);
7372  Cell::VisitGridObjects(m_bot, checker, float(m_collectDist));
7373 
7374  // no objects found, continue to next entry
7375  if (tempTargetGOList.empty())
7376  continue;
7377 
7378  // add any objects found to our lootTargets
7379  for (GameObjectList::iterator iter = tempTargetGOList.begin(); iter != tempTargetGOList.end(); iter++)
7380  {
7381  GameObject* go = (*iter);
7382 
7383  TerrainInfo const* map = go->GetTerrain();
7384 
7385  float ground_z = map->GetHeightStatic(go->GetPositionX(), go->GetPositionY(), go->GetPositionZ());
7386  // DEBUG_LOG("ground_z (%f) > INVALID_HEIGHT (%f)",ground_z,INVALID_HEIGHT);
7387  if ((ground_z > INVALID_HEIGHT) && go->IsSpawned())
7388  m_lootTargets.push_back(go->GetObjectGuid());
7389  }
7390  }
7391 }
7392 
7393 void PlayerbotAI::findNearbyCorpse()
7394 {
7395  UnitList corpseList;
7396  float radius = float(m_mgr.m_confCollectDistance);
7397  MaNGOS::AnyDeadUnitCheck corpse_check(m_bot);
7398  MaNGOS::UnitListSearcher<MaNGOS::AnyDeadUnitCheck> reaper(corpseList, corpse_check);
7399  Cell::VisitAllObjects(m_bot, reaper, radius);
7400 
7401  //if (!corpseList.empty())
7402  // TellMaster("Found %i Corpse(s)", corpseList.size());
7403 
7404  for (UnitList::const_iterator i = corpseList.begin(); i != corpseList.end(); ++i)
7405  {
7406  Creature* corpse = (Creature*)*i;
7407  if (!corpse)
7408  continue;
7409 
7410  if (!corpse->IsCorpse() || corpse->IsDespawned() || m_bot->CanAssist(corpse) || !corpse->m_loot)
7411  continue;
7412 
7413  if (!corpse->m_loot->CanLoot(m_bot) && !corpse->HasFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_SKINNABLE))
7414  continue;
7415 
7416  uint32 skillId = 0;
7417  if (corpse->HasFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_SKINNABLE))
7418  skillId = corpse->GetCreatureInfo()->GetRequiredLootSkill();
7419 
7420  if (corpse->HasFlag(UNIT_DYNAMIC_FLAGS, UNIT_DYNFLAG_LOOTABLE) ||
7421  (corpse->HasFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_SKINNABLE) && m_bot->HasSkill(skillId)))
7422  {
7423  m_lootTargets.push_back(corpse->GetObjectGuid());
7424  m_lootTargets.unique();
7425  }
7426  }
7427 }
7428 
7429 void PlayerbotAI::findNearbyCreature()
7430 {
7431  // Do not waste time finding a creature if bot has nothing to do
7432  // and clear list (sanity check)
7433  if (m_tasks.empty())
7434  {
7435  m_findNPC.clear();
7436  return;
7437  }
7438  CreatureList creatureList;
7439  float radius = INTERACTION_DISTANCE;
7440 
7441  CellPair pair(MaNGOS::ComputeCellPair(m_bot->GetPositionX(), m_bot->GetPositionY()));
7442  Cell cell(pair);
7443 
7444  MaNGOS::AnyUnitInObjectRangeCheck go_check(m_bot, radius);
7445  MaNGOS::CreatureListSearcher<MaNGOS::AnyUnitInObjectRangeCheck> go_search(creatureList, go_check);
7446  TypeContainerVisitor<MaNGOS::CreatureListSearcher<MaNGOS::AnyUnitInObjectRangeCheck>, GridTypeMapContainer> go_visit(go_search);
7447 
7448  // Get Creatures
7449  cell.Visit(pair, go_visit, *(m_bot->GetMap()), *(m_bot), radius);
7450 
7451  // if (!creatureList.empty())
7452  // TellMaster("Found %i Creatures & size of m_findNPC (%i)", creatureList.size(),m_findNPC.size());
7453 
7454  for (CreatureList::iterator iter = creatureList.begin(); iter != creatureList.end(); iter++)
7455  {
7456  Creature* currCreature = *iter;
7457 
7458  for (std::list<enum NPCFlags>::iterator itr = m_findNPC.begin(); itr != m_findNPC.end();)
7459  {
7460  uint32 npcflags = currCreature->GetUInt32Value(UNIT_NPC_FLAGS);
7461 
7462  if (!(*itr & npcflags))
7463  {
7464  ++itr;
7465  continue;
7466  }
7467 
7468  if ((*itr == UNIT_NPC_FLAG_TRAINER_CLASS) && !currCreature->CanTrainAndResetTalentsOf(m_bot))
7469  break;
7470 
7471  WorldObject* wo = m_bot->GetMap()->GetWorldObject(currCreature->GetObjectGuid());
7472 
7473  if (m_bot->GetDistance(wo) > CONTACT_DISTANCE + wo->GetObjectBoundingRadius())
7474  {
7475  float x, y, z;
7476  wo->GetContactPoint(m_bot, x, y, z, wo->GetObjectBoundingRadius());
7477  m_bot->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(wo->GetMapId(), x, y, z, FORCED_MOVEMENT_RUN, false);
7478  // give time to move to point before trying again
7479  SetIgnoreUpdateTime(1);
7480  }
7481 
7482  if (m_bot->GetDistance(wo) < INTERACTION_DISTANCE)
7483  {
7484  // DEBUG_LOG("%s is interacting with (%s)",m_bot->GetName(),currCreature->GetCreatureInfo()->Name);
7485  // Stop moving as soon as bot is in range
7486  m_bot->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(false);
7487  m_bot->GetMotionMaster()->MoveIdle();
7488  GossipMenuItemsMapBounds pMenuItemBounds = sObjectMgr.GetGossipMenuItemsMapBounds(currCreature->GetCreatureInfo()->GossipMenuId);
7489 
7490  // prepares quest menu when true
7491  bool canSeeQuests = currCreature->GetCreatureInfo()->GossipMenuId == m_bot->GetDefaultGossipMenuForSource(wo);
7492 
7493  // if canSeeQuests (the default, top level menu) and no menu options exist for this, use options from default options
7494  if (pMenuItemBounds.first == pMenuItemBounds.second && canSeeQuests)
7495  pMenuItemBounds = sObjectMgr.GetGossipMenuItemsMapBounds(0);
7496 
7497  for (GossipMenuItemsMap::const_iterator it = pMenuItemBounds.first; it != pMenuItemBounds.second; it++)
7498  {
7499  if (!(it->second.npc_option_npcflag & npcflags))
7500  continue;
7501 
7502  switch (it->second.option_id)
7503  {
7504  case GOSSIP_OPTION_BANKER:
7505  {
7506  // Manage banking actions
7507  if (!m_tasks.empty())
7508  for (std::list<taskPair>::iterator ait = m_tasks.begin(); ait != m_tasks.end(); ait = m_tasks.erase(ait))
7509  {
7510  switch (ait->first)
7511  {
7512  // withdraw items
7513  case BANK_WITHDRAW:
7514  {
7515  // TellMaster("Withdraw items");
7516  if (!Withdraw(ait->second))
7517  DEBUG_LOG("Withdraw: Couldn't withdraw (%u)", ait->second);
7518  break;
7519  }
7520  // deposit items
7521  case BANK_DEPOSIT:
7522  {
7523  // TellMaster("Deposit items");
7524  if (!Deposit(ait->second))
7525  DEBUG_LOG("Deposit: Couldn't deposit (%u)", ait->second);
7526  break;
7527  }
7528  default:
7529  break;
7530  }
7531  }
7532  BankBalance();
7533  break;
7534  }
7535  case GOSSIP_OPTION_TAXIVENDOR:
7536  case GOSSIP_OPTION_GOSSIP:
7537  case GOSSIP_OPTION_INNKEEPER:
7538  case GOSSIP_OPTION_TRAINER:
7539  case GOSSIP_OPTION_QUESTGIVER:
7540  case GOSSIP_OPTION_VENDOR:
7541  case GOSSIP_OPTION_UNLEARNTALENTS:
7542  case GOSSIP_OPTION_ARMORER:
7543  {
7544  // Manage questgiver, trainer, innkeeper & vendor actions
7545  if (!m_tasks.empty())
7546  for (std::list<taskPair>::iterator ait = m_tasks.begin(); ait != m_tasks.end(); ait = m_tasks.erase(ait))
7547  {
7548  switch (ait->first)
7549  {
7550  // reset talents
7551  case RESET_TALENTS:
7552  {
7553  // TellMaster("Reset all talents");
7554  if (Talent(currCreature))
7555  InspectUpdate();
7556  break;
7557  }
7558  // take new quests
7559  case TAKE_QUEST:
7560  {
7561  // TellMaster("Accepting quest");
7562  if (!AddQuest(ait->second, wo))
7563  DEBUG_LOG("AddQuest: Couldn't add quest (%u)", ait->second);
7564  break;
7565  }
7566  // list npc quests
7567  case LIST_QUEST:
7568  {
7569  // TellMaster("Show available npc quests");
7570  ListQuests(wo);
7571  break;
7572  }
7573  // end quests
7574  case END_QUEST:
7575  {
7576  // TellMaster("Turn in available quests");
7577  TurnInQuests(wo);
7578  break;
7579  }
7580  // sell items
7581  case SELL_ITEMS:
7582  {
7583  // TellMaster("Selling items");
7584  Sell(ait->second);
7585  break;
7586  }
7587  // buy items
7588  case BUY_ITEMS:
7589  {
7590  // TellMaster("Buying items");
7591  Buy(currCreature, ait->second);
7592  break;
7593  }
7594  // repair items
7595  case REPAIR_ITEMS:
7596  {
7597  // TellMaster("Repairing items");
7598  Repair(ait->second, currCreature);
7599  break;
7600  }
7601  default:
7602  break;
7603  }
7604  }
7605  break;
7606  }
7607  case GOSSIP_OPTION_AUCTIONEER:
7608  {
7609  // Manage auctioneer actions
7610  if (!m_tasks.empty())
7611  for (std::list<taskPair>::iterator ait = m_tasks.begin(); ait != m_tasks.end(); ait = m_tasks.erase(ait))
7612  {
7613  switch (ait->first)
7614  {
7615  // add new auction item
7616  case ADD_AUCTION:
7617  {
7618  // TellMaster("Creating auction");
7619  AddAuction(ait->second, currCreature);
7620  break;
7621  }
7622  // cancel active auction
7623  case REMOVE_AUCTION:
7624  {
7625  // TellMaster("Cancelling auction");
7626  if (!RemoveAuction(ait->second))
7627  DEBUG_LOG("RemoveAuction: Couldn't remove auction (%u)", ait->second);
7628  break;
7629  }
7630  default:
7631  break;
7632  }
7633  }
7634  ListAuctions();
7635  break;
7636  }
7637  default:
7638  break;
7639  }
7640  AutoUpgradeEquipment();
7641  m_bot->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_TALK);
7642  }
7643  itr = m_findNPC.erase(itr); // all done lets go home
7644  continue;
7645  }
7646  ++itr;
7647  }
7648  }
7649 }

7656 {
7657  // Talent function in Player::GetLevel take care of resetting talents in case level < getLevel()
7658  ApplyActiveTalentSpec();
7659 }

7671 bool PlayerbotAI::IsElite(Unit* target, bool isWorldBoss) const
7672 {
7673  if (!target || target->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
7674  return false;
7675 
7676  if (Creature* creature = (Creature*) target)
7677  {
7678  if (isWorldBoss)
7679  return creature->IsWorldBoss();
7680  else
7681  return (creature->IsElite() || creature->IsWorldBoss());
7682  }
7683 
7684  return false;
7685 }

7687 // Check if bot target has one of the following auras: Sap, Polymorph, Shackle Undead, Banish, Seduction, Freezing Trap, Hibernate
7688 // This is used by the AI to prevent bots from attacking crowd control targets
7689 
7690 static const uint32 aurasIds[21] =
7691 {
7692  118, 12824, 12825, 12826, // polymorph
7693  28272, 28271, // polymorph pig, turtle
7694  9484, 9485, 10955, // shackle
7695  6358, // seduction
7696  710, 18647, // banish
7697  6770, 2070, 11297, // sap
7698  3355, 14308, 14309, // freezing trap (effect auras IDs, not spell IDs)
7699  2637, 18657, 18658 // hibernate
7700 };

7702 bool PlayerbotAI::IsNeutralized(Unit* target)
7703 {

7705  return false;
7706 
7707  for (auto aura : aurasIds)
7708  {
7709  if (target->HasAura(aura, EFFECT_INDEX_0))
7710  return true;
7711  }
7712 
7713  return false;
7714 }

7750 bool PlayerbotAI::CanStore()
7751 {
7752  uint32 totalused = 0;
7753  // list out items in main backpack
7754  for (uint8 slot = INVENTORY_SLOT_ITEM_START; slot < INVENTORY_SLOT_ITEM_END; slot++)
7755  {
7756  const Item* const pItem = m_bot->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, slot);
7757  if (pItem)
7758  totalused++;
7759  }
7760  uint32 totalfree = 16 - totalused;
7761  // list out items in other removable backpacks
7762  for (uint8 bag = INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_START; bag < INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_END; ++bag)
7763  {
7764  const Bag* const pBag = (Bag*) m_bot->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, bag);
7765  if (pBag)
7766  {
7767  ItemPrototype const* pBagProto = pBag->GetProto();
7768  if (pBagProto->Class == ITEM_CLASS_CONTAINER && pBagProto->SubClass == ITEM_SUBCLASS_CONTAINER)
7769  totalfree = totalfree + pBag->GetFreeSlots();
7770  }
7771  }
7772  return totalfree > 0;
7773 }

7802 
7803 // generic item use method
7804 void PlayerbotAI::UseItem(Item* item, uint32 targetFlag, ObjectGuid targetGUID)
7805 {
7806  if (!item)
7807  return;
7808 
7809  uint8 bagIndex = item->GetBagSlot();
7810  uint8 slot = item->GetSlot();
7811  uint8 cast_count = 1;
7812  ObjectGuid item_guid = item->GetObjectGuid();
7813  uint32 glyphIndex = 0;
7814  uint8 unk_flags = 0;
7815 
7816  if (uint32 questid = item->GetProto()->StartQuest)
7817  {
7818  std::ostringstream report;
7819 
7820  Quest const* qInfo = sObjectMgr.GetQuestTemplate(questid);
7821  if (qInfo)
7822  {
7823  m_bot->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(true);
7824  std::unique_ptr<WorldPacket> packet(new WorldPacket(CMSG_QUESTGIVER_ACCEPT_QUEST, 8 + 4 + 4));
7825  *packet << item_guid;
7826  *packet << questid;
7827  *packet << uint32(0);
7828  m_bot->GetSession()->QueuePacket(std::move(packet)); // queue the packet to get around race condition
7829  report << "|cffffff00Quest taken |r" << qInfo->GetTitle();
7830  TellMaster(report.str());
7831  }
7832  return;
7833  }
7834 
7835  uint32 spellId = 0;
7836  for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_ITEM_PROTO_SPELLS; ++i)
7837  {
7838  if (item->GetProto()->Spells[i].SpellId > 0)
7839  {
7840  spellId = item->GetProto()->Spells[i].SpellId;
7841  break;
7842  }
7843  }
7844 
7845  if (item->GetProto()->Flags & ITEM_FLAG_HAS_LOOT && spellId == 0)
7846  {
7847  // Open quest item in inventory, containing related items (e.g Gnarlpine necklace, containing Tallonkai's Jewel)
7848  std::unique_ptr<WorldPacket> packet(new WorldPacket(CMSG_OPEN_ITEM, 2));
7849  *packet << item->GetBagSlot();
7850  *packet << item->GetSlot();
7851  m_bot->GetSession()->QueuePacket(std::move(packet)); // queue the packet to get around race condition
7852  return;
7853  }
7854 
7855  std::unique_ptr<WorldPacket> packet(new WorldPacket(CMSG_USE_ITEM, 28));
7856  *packet << bagIndex << slot << cast_count << spellId << item_guid
7857  << glyphIndex << unk_flags << targetFlag;
7858 
7859  if (targetFlag & (TARGET_FLAG_UNIT | TARGET_FLAG_ITEM | TARGET_FLAG_GAMEOBJECT))
7860  *packet << targetGUID.WriteAsPacked();
7861 
7862  m_bot->GetSession()->QueuePacket(std::move(packet));
7863 
7864  SpellEntry const* spellInfo = sSpellTemplate.LookupEntry<SpellEntry>(spellId);
7865  if (!spellInfo)
7866  {
7867  TellMaster("Can't find spell entry for spell %u on item %u", spellId, item->GetEntry());
7868  return;
7869  }
7870 
7871  SpellCastTimesEntry const* castingTimeEntry = sSpellCastTimesStore.LookupEntry(spellInfo->CastingTimeIndex);
7872  if (!castingTimeEntry)
7873  {
7874  TellMaster("Can't find casting time entry for spell %u with index %u", spellId, spellInfo->CastingTimeIndex);
7875  return;
7876  }
7877 
7878  uint8 duration, castTime;
7879  castTime = (uint8)((float) castingTimeEntry->CastTime / 1000.0f);
7880 
7881  if (item->GetProto()->Class == ITEM_CLASS_CONSUMABLE && item->GetProto()->SubClass == ITEM_SUBCLASS_FOOD)
7882  {
7883  duration = (uint8)((float) GetSpellDuration(spellInfo) / 1000.0f);
7884  SetIgnoreUpdateTime(castTime + duration);
7885  }
7886  else
7887  SetIgnoreUpdateTime(castTime);
7888 }
7889 
7890 static const uint32 uPriorizedHealingItemIds[19] =
7891 {
7892  HEALTHSTONE_DISPLAYID, FEL_REGENERATION_POTION, SUPER_HEALING_POTION, CRYSTAL_HEALING_POTION, MAJOR_DREAMLESS_SLEEP_POTION, VOLATILE_HEALING_POTION,
7893  MAJOR_HEALING_POTION, WHIPPER_ROOT_TUBER, NIGHT_DRAGON_BREATH, LIMITED_INVULNERABILITY_POTION, GREATER_DREAMLESS_SLEEP_POTION,
7894  SUPERIOR_HEALING_POTION, CRYSTAL_RESTORE, DREAMLESS_SLEEP_POTION, GREATER_HEALING_POTION, HEALING_POTION, LESSER_HEALING_POTION, DISCOLORED_HEALING_POTION, MINOR_HEALING_POTION,
7895 };
7896 
7904 void PlayerbotAI::TryEmergency(Unit* pAttacker)
7905 {
7906  // Do not use consumable if bot can heal self
7907  if (IsHealer() && GetManaPercent() > 20)
7908  return;
7909 
7910  // If bot does not have aggro: use bandage instead of potion/stone/crystal
7911  if (!pAttacker && !m_bot->HasAura(11196)) // Recently bandaged
7912  {
7913  Item* bandage = FindBandage();
7914  if (bandage)
7915  {
7916  SetIgnoreUpdateTime(8);
7917  UseItem(bandage);
7918  return;
7919  }
7920  }
7921 
7922  // Else loop over the list of health consumable to pick one
7923  Item* healthItem;
7924  for (uint8 i = 0; i < countof(uPriorizedHealingItemIds); ++i)
7925  {
7926  healthItem = FindConsumable(uPriorizedHealingItemIds[i]);
7927  if (healthItem)
7928  {
7929  UseItem(healthItem);
7930  return;
7931  }
7932  }
7933 
7934  return;
7935 }
7936 
7937 // submits packet to use an item
7938 void PlayerbotAI::EquipItem(Item* src_Item)
7939 {
7940  uint8 src_bagIndex = src_Item->GetBagSlot();
7941  uint8 src_slot = src_Item->GetSlot();
7942 
7943  // DEBUG_LOG("PlayerbotAI::EquipItem: %s in srcbag = %u, srcslot = %u", src_Item->GetProto()->Name1, src_bagIndex, src_slot);
7944 
7945  uint16 dest;
7946  InventoryResult msg = m_bot->CanEquipItem(NULL_SLOT, dest, src_Item, !src_Item->IsBag());
7947  if (msg != EQUIP_ERR_OK)
7948  {
7949  m_bot->SendEquipError(msg, src_Item, nullptr);
7950  return;
7951  }
7952 
7953  uint16 src = src_Item->GetPos();
7954  if (dest == src) // prevent equip in same slot, only at cheat
7955  return;
7956 
7957  Item* dest_Item = m_bot->GetItemByPos(dest);
7958  if (!dest_Item) // empty slot, simple case
7959  {
7960  m_bot->RemoveItem(src_bagIndex, src_slot, true);
7961  m_bot->EquipItem(dest, src_Item, true);
7962  m_bot->AutoUnequipOffhandIfNeed();
7963  }
7964  else // have currently equipped item, not simple case
7965  {
7966  uint8 dest_bagIndex = dest_Item->GetBagSlot();
7967  uint8 dest_slot = dest_Item->GetSlot();
7968 
7969  msg = m_bot->CanUnequipItem(dest, false);
7970  if (msg != EQUIP_ERR_OK)
7971  {
7972  m_bot->SendEquipError(msg, dest_Item, nullptr);
7973  return;
7974  }
7975 
7976  // check dest->src move possibility
7977  ItemPosCountVec sSrc;
7978  if (m_bot->IsInventoryPos(src))
7979  {
7980  msg = m_bot->CanStoreItem(src_bagIndex, src_slot, sSrc, dest_Item, true);
7981  if (msg != EQUIP_ERR_OK)
7982  msg = m_bot->CanStoreItem(src_bagIndex, NULL_SLOT, sSrc, dest_Item, true);
7983  if (msg != EQUIP_ERR_OK)
7984  msg = m_bot->CanStoreItem(NULL_BAG, NULL_SLOT, sSrc, dest_Item, true);
7985  }
7986 
7987  if (msg != EQUIP_ERR_OK)
7988  {
7989  m_bot->SendEquipError(msg, dest_Item, src_Item);
7990  return;
7991  }
7992 
7993  // now do moves, remove...
7994  m_bot->RemoveItem(dest_bagIndex, dest_slot, false);
7995  m_bot->RemoveItem(src_bagIndex, src_slot, false);
7996 
7997  // add to dest
7998  m_bot->EquipItem(dest, src_Item, true);
7999 
8000  // add to src
8001  if (m_bot->IsInventoryPos(src))
8002  m_bot->StoreItem(sSrc, dest_Item, true);
8003 
8004  m_bot->AutoUnequipOffhandIfNeed();
8005  }
8006 }
8007 
8008 // submits packet to trade an item (trade window must already be open)
8009 // default slot is -1 which means trade slots 0 to 5. if slot is set
8010 // to TRADE_SLOT_NONTRADED (which is slot 6) item will be shown in the
8011 // 'Will not be traded' slot.
8012 bool PlayerbotAI::TradeItem(const Item& item, int8 slot)
8013 {
8014  // DEBUG_LOG ("[PlayerbotAI]: TradeItem - slot=%d, hasTrader=%d, itemInTrade=%d, itemTradeable=%d",
8015  // slot,
8016  // (m_bot->GetTrader() ? 1 : 0),
8017  // (item.IsInTrade() ? 1 : 0),
8018  // (item.CanBeTraded() ? 1 : 0)
8019  // );
8020 
8021  if (!m_bot->GetTrader() || item.IsInTrade() || (!item.CanBeTraded() && slot != TRADE_SLOT_NONTRADED))
8022  return false;
8023 
8024  int8 tradeSlot = -1;
8025 
8026  TradeData* pTrade = m_bot->GetTradeData();
8027  if ((slot >= 0 && slot < TRADE_SLOT_COUNT) && pTrade->GetItem(TradeSlots(slot)) == nullptr)
8028  tradeSlot = slot;
8029  else
8030  for (uint8 i = 0; i < TRADE_SLOT_TRADED_COUNT && tradeSlot == -1; i++)
8031  {
8032  if (pTrade->GetItem(TradeSlots(i)) == nullptr)
8033  {
8034  tradeSlot = i;
8035  // reserve trade slot to allow multiple items to be traded
8036  pTrade->SetItem(TradeSlots(i), const_cast<Item*>(&item));
8037  }
8038  }
8039 
8040  if (tradeSlot == -1) return false;
8041 
8042  std::unique_ptr<WorldPacket> packet(new WorldPacket(CMSG_SET_TRADE_ITEM, 3));
8043  *packet << (uint8) tradeSlot << (uint8) item.GetBagSlot()
8044  << (uint8) item.GetSlot();
8045  m_bot->GetSession()->QueuePacket(std::move(packet));
8046  return true;
8047 }
8048 
8049 // submits packet to trade copper (trade window must be open)
8050 bool PlayerbotAI::TradeCopper(uint32 copper)
8051 {
8052  if (copper > 0)
8053  {
8054  std::unique_ptr<WorldPacket> packet(new WorldPacket(CMSG_SET_TRADE_GOLD, 4));
8055  *packet << copper;
8056  m_bot->GetSession()->QueuePacket(std::move(packet));
8057  return true;
8058  }
8059  return false;
8060 }

8062 bool PlayerbotAI::DoTeleport(WorldObject& /*obj*/)

8074  ch.sysmessage(".. could not be teleported ..");
8075  // DEBUG_LOG ("[PlayerbotAI]: DoTeleport - %s failed to teleport", m_bot->GetName() );
8076  return false;
8077  }
8078  return true;
8079 }

8082 void PlayerbotAI::ItemLocalization(std::string& itemName, const uint32 itemID) const
8083 {

8089  if (pItemInfo->Name.size() > loc && !pItemInfo->Name[loc].empty())

8094  }
8095 }

8127 void PlayerbotAI::GameObjectLocalization(std::string& gameobjectName, const uint32 entry) const
8128 {
8129  uint32 loc = GetMaster()->GetSession()->GetSessionDbLocaleIndex();
8130  std::wstring wnamepart;
8131 
8132  GameObjectLocale const* pGameObjectInfo = sObjectMgr.GetGameObjectLocale(entry);
8133  if (pGameObjectInfo)

8139  }

8142 // Helper function for automatically selling poor quality items to the vendor
8143 void PlayerbotAI::_doSellItem(Item* const item, std::ostringstream& report, std::ostringstream& canSell, uint32& TotalCost, uint32& TotalSold)
8144 {
8145  if (!item)
8146  return;
8147 
8148  uint8 autosell = 0;
8149  ItemPrototype const* pProto = item->GetProto();
8150 
8151  std::ostringstream mout;
8152  if (item->CanBeTraded() && pProto->Quality == ITEM_QUALITY_POOR) // trash sells automatically.
8153  autosell = 1;
8154 
8155  if (SellWhite == 1) // set this with the command 'sell all'
8156  {
8157  // here we'll do some checks for other items that are safe to automatically sell such as
8158  // white items that are a number of levels lower than anything we could possibly use.
8159  // We'll check to make sure its not a tradeskill tool, quest item etc, things that we don't want to lose.
8160  if (pProto->SellPrice > 0 && (pProto->Quality == ITEM_QUALITY_NORMAL || pProto->Quality == ITEM_QUALITY_UNCOMMON) && pProto->SubClass != ITEM_SUBCLASS_QUEST)
8161  {
8162  if (pProto->RequiredLevel < (m_bot->GetLevel() - m_mgr.gConfigSellLevelDiff) && pProto->SubClass != ITEM_SUBCLASS_WEAPON_MISC && pProto->FoodType == 0)
8163  {
8164  if (pProto->Class == ITEM_CLASS_WEAPON)
8165  autosell = 1;
8166  if (pProto->Class == ITEM_CLASS_ARMOR)
8167  autosell = 1;
8168  }
8169  if (pProto->SubClass == ITEM_SUBCLASS_FOOD && (pProto->RequiredLevel < (m_bot->GetLevel() - m_mgr.gConfigSellLevelDiff)))
8170  {
8171  autosell = 1;
8172  }
8173  }
8174  }
8175 
8176  if (autosell == 1) // set this switch above and this item gets sold automatically. Only set this for automatic sales e.g junk etc.
8177  {
8178 
8179 
8180  uint32 cost = pProto->SellPrice * item->GetCount();
8181 
8182  // handle spell charge if any
8183  for (auto i = 0; i < MAX_ITEM_PROTO_SPELLS; ++i)
8184  {
8185  auto const& spell = pProto->Spells[i];
8186 
8187  // if spell charges for this item are negative, it means that the item should be destroyed once the charges are consumed.
8188  // it also means that the value of this item is relative to how many charges are remaining.
8189  if (spell.SpellId != 0 && spell.SpellCharges < 0)
8190  {
8191  auto const multiplier = static_cast<float>(item->GetSpellCharges(i)) / spell.SpellCharges;
8192  cost *= multiplier;
8193  break;
8194  }
8195  }
8196 
8197  m_bot->MoveItemFromInventory(item->GetBagSlot(), item->GetSlot(), true);
8198  m_bot->AddItemToBuyBackSlot(item, cost);
8199  m_bot->ModifyMoney(cost);
8200 
8201  ++TotalSold;
8202  TotalCost += cost;
8203 
8204  report << "Sold ";
8205  MakeItemLink(item, report, true);
8206  report << " for " << Cash(cost);
8207  }
8208  else if (pProto->SellPrice > 0)
8209  MakeItemLink(item, canSell, true);
8210 }

8217  std::ostringstream report;
8218

8221  if (msg != EQUIP_ERR_OK)
8222  {
8223  m_bot->SendEquipError(msg, pItem, nullptr);
8224  return false;
8225  }
8226 
8227  m_bot->RemoveItem(pItem->GetBagSlot(), pItem->GetSlot(), true);
8228  m_bot->StoreItem(dest, pItem, true);
8229 
8230  report << "Withdrawn ";
8231  MakeItemLink(pItem, report, true);
8232 
8233  TellMaster(report.str());
8234  }
8235  return true;

8328 void PlayerbotAI::Repair(const uint32 itemid, Creature* rCreature)
8329 {
8330  uint32 cost = 0;
8331  uint8 UseGuild = (m_bot->GetGuildId() != 0) ? uint8(1) : uint8(0);
8332  Item* rItem = FindItem(itemid, true); // if item equipped or in bags
8333  if (rItem)
8334  cost = EstRepair(rItem->GetPos());
8335  else
8336  cost = EstRepairAll();
8337 
8338  Guild* pGuild = sGuildMgr.GetGuildById(m_bot->GetGuildId());
8339 
8340  if (pGuild)
8341  {
8342  // Check whether bot can use the guildbank first
8343  if (!pGuild->HasRankRight(m_bot->GetRank(), GR_RIGHT_WITHDRAW_REPAIR))
8344  {
8345  DEBUG_LOG("You do not have rights to withdraw for repairs");
8346  UseGuild = 0;
8347  }
8348 
8349  if (pGuild->GetGuildBankMoney() < cost)
8350  {
8351  DEBUG_LOG("There is not enough money in the guild bank");
8352  UseGuild = 0;
8353  }
8354  }
8355 
8356  // If guildbank unavailable, check pockets
8357  if (UseGuild == 0)
8358  if (m_bot->GetMoney() < cost)
8359  {
8360  TellMaster("I do not have enough money to repair");
8361  return;
8362  }
8363 
8364  ObjectGuid itemGuid = (rItem) ? rItem->GetObjectGuid() : ObjectGuid();
8365 
8366  std::unique_ptr<WorldPacket> packet(new WorldPacket(CMSG_REPAIR_ITEM, 8 + 8 + 1));
8367  *packet << rCreature->GetObjectGuid(); // repair npc guid
8368  *packet << itemGuid; // if item specified then repair this, else repair all
8369  *packet << UseGuild; // guildbank yes=1 no=0
8370  m_bot->GetSession()->QueuePacket(std::move(packet)); // queue the packet to get around race condition
8371 }

8373 bool PlayerbotAI::RemoveAuction(const uint32 auctionid)
8374 {
8375  QueryResult* result = CharacterDatabase.PQuery(
8376  "SELECT houseid,itemguid,item_template,itemowner,buyoutprice,time,buyguid,lastbid,startbid,deposit FROM auction WHERE id = '%u'", auctionid);
8377 
8378  AuctionEntry* auction;
8379 
8380  if (result)
8381  {
8382  Field* fields = result->Fetch();
8383 
8384  auction = new AuctionEntry;
8385  auction->Id = auctionid;
8386  uint32 houseid = fields[0].GetUInt32();
8387  auction->itemGuidLow = fields[1].GetUInt32();
8388  auction->itemTemplate = fields[2].GetUInt32();
8389  auction->owner = fields[3].GetUInt32();
8390  auction->buyout = fields[4].GetUInt32();
8391  auction->expireTime = fields[5].GetUInt32();
8392  auction->bidder = fields[6].GetUInt32();
8393  auction->bid = fields[7].GetUInt32();
8394  auction->startbid = fields[8].GetUInt32();
8395  auction->deposit = fields[9].GetUInt32();
8396  auction->auctionHouseEntry = nullptr; // init later
8397 
8398  // check if sold item exists for guid
8399  // and item_template in fact (GetAItem will fail if problematic in result check in AuctionHouseMgr::LoadAuctionItems)
8400  Item* pItem = sAuctionMgr.GetAItem(auction->itemGuidLow);
8401  if (!pItem)
8402  {
8403  auction->DeleteFromDB();
8404  sLog.outError("Auction %u has not a existing item : %u, deleted", auction->Id, auction->itemGuidLow);
8405  delete auction;
8406  delete result;
8407  return false;
8408  }
8409 
8410  auction->auctionHouseEntry = sAuctionHouseStore.LookupEntry(houseid);
8411 
8412  // Attempt send item back to owner
8413  std::ostringstream msgAuctionCanceledOwner;
8414  msgAuctionCanceledOwner << auction->itemTemplate << ":0:" << AUCTION_CANCELED << ":0:0";
8415 
8416  // item will deleted or added to received mail list
8417  MailDraft(msgAuctionCanceledOwner.str(), "") // TODO: fix body
8418  .AddItem(pItem)
8419  .SendMailTo(MailReceiver(ObjectGuid(HIGHGUID_PLAYER, auction->owner)), auction, MAIL_CHECK_MASK_COPIED);
8420 
8421  if (sAuctionMgr.RemoveAItem(auction->itemGuidLow))
8422  m_bot->GetSession()->SendAuctionCommandResult(auction, AUCTION_REMOVED, AUCTION_OK);
8423 
8424  auction->DeleteFromDB();
8425 
8426  delete auction;
8427  delete result;
8428  }
8429  return true;
8430 }

8432 // Subject - 9360:0:2

8437 std::string PlayerbotAI::AuctionResult(std::string subject, std::string body)
8438 {
8439  std::ostringstream out;
8440  std::string winner;
8441  int pos;
8442 
8443  subject.append(":");
8444  if (body.size() > 0)
8445  {
8446  pos = body.find_first_not_of(" ");
8447  subject.append(body, pos, body.size() - pos);
8448  subject.append(":");
8449  }
8450 
8451  // DEBUG_LOG("Auctions string (%s)", subject.c_str());
8452  pos = 0;
8453  int sublen = subject.size() / 2;
8454  uint32 a_info[15];
8455  for (int i = 0; i < sublen; i++)
8456  {
8457  int endpos = subject.find(':', pos);
8458  std::string idc = subject.substr(pos, endpos - pos);
8459  a_info[i] = atol(idc.c_str());
8460  // DEBUG_LOG("a_info[%d] = (%u)", i, a_info[i]);
8461  pos = endpos + 1;
8462  }
8463 
8464  if (a_info[4] != a_info[5])
8465  winner = "High Bidder";
8466  else
8467  winner = "Buyout";
8468 
8469  ItemPrototype const* pProto = ObjectMgr::GetItemPrototype(a_info[0]);
8470  if (!pProto)
8471  return out.str();
8472 
8473  switch (a_info[2])
8474  {
8475  case AUCTION_OUTBIDDED: //= 0,
8476  out << "Subject: Outbid on: " << pProto->Name1;
8477  break;
8478  case AUCTION_WON: //= 1,
8479  out << "Subject: Auction won: " << pProto->Name1 << "\n";
8480  out << "Item Purchased: " << pProto->Name1 << "\n";
8481  break;
8482  case AUCTION_SUCCESSFUL: //= 2,
8483  {
8484  out << "Subject: Auction successful: " << pProto->Name1 << "\n";
8485  out << "Item Sold: " << pProto->Name1 << "\n";
8486  out << "\n[" << winner << " Sale: " << Cash(a_info[4]) << "]";
8487  out << "\n( |cff1eff00Deposit:|cffccffff " << Cash(a_info[6]) << " |cffff0000- Tax:|cffccffff " << Cash(a_info[7]) << " ) |cff1eff00+|cffccffff";
8488  break;
8489  }
8490  case AUCTION_EXPIRED: //= 3,
8491  out << "Subject: Auction expired: " << pProto->Name1;
8492  break;
8493  case AUCTION_CANCELLED_TO_BIDDER: //= 4,
8494  out << "Subject: Auction cancelled to bidder: " << pProto->Name1;
8495  break;
8496  case AUCTION_CANCELED: //= 5,
8497  out << "Subject: Auction cancelled: " << pProto->Name1;
8498  break;
8499  case AUCTION_SALE_PENDING: //= 6
8500  out << "Subject: Auction sale pending: " << pProto->Name1;
8501  break;
8502  }
8503  return out.str();
8504 }

8506 std::string PlayerbotAI::Cash(uint32 copper)
8507 {
8508  using namespace std;
8509  std::ostringstream change;
8510 
8511  uint32 gold = uint32(copper / 10000);
8512  copper -= (gold * 10000);
8513  uint32 silver = uint32(copper / 100);
8514  copper -= (silver * 100);
8515 
8516  if (gold > 0)
8517  change << gold << " |TInterface\\Icons\\INV_Misc_Coin_01:8|t";
8518  if (silver > 0)
8519  change << std::setfill(' ') << std::setw(2) << silver << " |TInterface\\Icons\\INV_Misc_Coin_03:8|t";
8520  change << std::setfill(' ') << std::setw(2) << copper << " |TInterface\\Icons\\INV_Misc_Coin_05:8|t";
8521 
8522  return change.str();
8523 }

8525 void PlayerbotAI::ListQuests(WorldObject* questgiver)
8526 {
8527  if (!questgiver)
8528  return;
8529 
8530  // list all bot quests this NPC has
8531  m_bot->PrepareQuestMenu(questgiver->GetObjectGuid());
8532  QuestMenu& questMenu = m_bot->GetPlayerMenu()->GetQuestMenu();
8533  std::ostringstream out;
8534  for (uint32 iI = 0; iI < questMenu.MenuItemCount(); ++iI)
8535  {
8536  QuestMenuItem const& qItem = questMenu.GetItem(iI);
8537  uint32 questID = qItem.m_qId;
8538  Quest const* pQuest = sObjectMgr.GetQuestTemplate(questID);
8539 
8540  if (m_bot->SatisfyQuestStatus(pQuest, false))
8541  {
8542  if (gQuestFetch != 1)
8543  {
8544  MakeQuestLink(pQuest, out);
8545  }
8546  else
8547  {
8548  if (!AddQuest(questID, questgiver))
8549  continue;
8550  }
8551  }
8552  }
8553  if (!out.str().empty())
8554  TellMaster(out.str());
8555 }

8557 bool PlayerbotAI::AddQuest(const uint32 entry, WorldObject* questgiver)
8558 {
8559  std::ostringstream out;
8560 
8561  Quest const* qInfo = sObjectMgr.GetQuestTemplate(entry);
8562  if (!qInfo)
8563  {
8564  ChatHandler(GetMaster()).PSendSysMessage(LANG_COMMAND_QUEST_NOTFOUND, entry);
8565  return false;
8566  }
8567 
8568  if (m_bot->GetQuestStatus(entry) == QUEST_STATUS_COMPLETE)
8569  {
8570  TellMaster("I already completed that quest.");
8571  return false;
8572  }
8573  else if (!m_bot->CanTakeQuest(qInfo, false))
8574  {
8575  if (!m_bot->SatisfyQuestStatus(qInfo, false))
8576  TellMaster("I already have that quest.");
8577  else
8578  TellMaster("I can't take that quest.");
8579  return false;
8580  }
8581  else if (!m_bot->SatisfyQuestLog(false))
8582  {
8583  TellMaster("My quest log is full.");
8584  return false;
8585  }
8586  else if (m_bot->CanAddQuest(qInfo, false))
8587  {
8588  m_bot->AddQuest(qInfo, questgiver);
8589 
8590  out << "|cffffff00Quest taken ";
8591  MakeQuestLink(qInfo, out);
8592 
8593  if (m_bot->CanCompleteQuest(entry))
8594  m_bot->CompleteQuest(entry);
8595 
8596  // build needed items if quest contains any
8597  for (int i = 0; i < QUEST_ITEM_OBJECTIVES_COUNT; i++)
8598  if (qInfo->ReqItemCount[i] > 0)
8599  {
8600  SetQuestNeedItems();
8601  break;
8602  }
8603 
8604  // build needed creatures if quest contains any
8605  for (int i = 0; i < QUEST_OBJECTIVES_COUNT; i++)
8606  if (qInfo->ReqCreatureOrGOCount[i] > 0)
8607  {
8608  SetQuestNeedCreatures();
8609  break;
8610  }
8611 
8612  TellMaster(out.str());
8613  return true;
8614  }
8615  return false;
8616 }

8618 void PlayerbotAI::ListAuctions()
8619 {
8620  std::ostringstream report;
8621 
8622  QueryResult* result = CharacterDatabase.PQuery(
8623  "SELECT id,itemguid,item_template,time,buyguid,lastbid FROM auction WHERE itemowner = '%u'", m_bot->GetObjectGuid().GetCounter());
8624  if (result)
8625  {
8626  report << "My active auctions are: \n";
8627  do
8628  {
8629  Field* fields = result->Fetch();
8630 
8631  uint32 Id = fields[0].GetUInt32();
8632  uint32 itemGuidLow = fields[1].GetUInt32();
8633  uint32 itemTemplate = fields[2].GetUInt32();
8634  time_t expireTime = fields[3].GetUInt32();
8635  uint32 bidder = fields[4].GetUInt32();
8636  uint32 bid = fields[5].GetUInt32();
8637 
8638  time_t remtime = expireTime - CurrentTime();
8639 
8640  tm* aTm = gmtime(&remtime);
8641 
8642  if (expireTime > CurrentTime())
8643  {
8644  Item* aItem = sAuctionMgr.GetAItem(itemGuidLow);
8645  if (aItem)
8646  {
8647  // Name
8648  uint32 count = aItem->GetCount();
8649  std::string name = aItem->GetProto()->Name1;
8650  ItemLocalization(name, itemTemplate);
8651  report << "\n|cffffffff|Htitle:" << Id << "|h[" << name;
8652  if (count > 1)
8653  report << "|cff00ff00x" << count << "|cffffffff" << "]|h|r";
8654  else
8655  report << "]|h|r";
8656  }
8657 
8658  if (bidder)
8659  {
8660  ObjectGuid guid = ObjectGuid(HIGHGUID_PLAYER, bidder);
8661  std::string bidder_name;
8662  if (sObjectMgr.GetPlayerNameByGUID(guid, bidder_name))
8663  report << " " << bidder_name << ": ";
8664 
8665  report << Cash(bid);
8666  }
8667  if (aItem)
8668  report << " ends: " << aTm->tm_hour << "|cff0070dd|hH|h|r " << aTm->tm_min << "|cff0070dd|hmin|h|r";
8669  }
8670  }
8671  while (result->NextRow());
8672 
8673  delete result;
8674  TellMaster(report.str().c_str());
8675  }
8676 }
8677 
8678 void PlayerbotAI::AddAuction(const uint32 itemid, Creature* aCreature)
8679 {
8680  Item* aItem = FindItem(itemid);
8681  if (aItem)
8682  {
8683  std::ostringstream out;
8684  srand(CurrentTime());
8685  uint32 duration[3] = { 720, 1440, 2880 }; // 720 = 12hrs, 1440 = 24hrs, 2880 = 48hrs
8686  uint32 etime = duration[rand() % 3];
8687 
8688  uint32 min = urand(aItem->GetProto()->SellPrice * aItem->GetCount(), aItem->GetProto()->BuyPrice * aItem->GetCount()) * (aItem->GetProto()->Quality + 1);
8689  uint32 max = urand(aItem->GetProto()->SellPrice * aItem->GetCount(), aItem->GetProto()->BuyPrice * aItem->GetCount()) * (aItem->GetProto()->Quality + 1);
8690 
8691  out << "Auctioning ";
8692  MakeItemLink(aItem, out, true);
8693  out << " with " << aCreature->GetCreatureInfo()->Name;
8694  TellMaster(out.str().c_str());
8695 
8696  std::unique_ptr<WorldPacket> packet(new WorldPacket(CMSG_AUCTION_SELL_ITEM, 8 + 4 + 8 + 4 + 4 + 4 + 4));
8697  *packet << aCreature->GetObjectGuid(); // auctioneer guid
8698  *packet << uint32(1); // const 1
8699  *packet << aItem->GetObjectGuid(); // item guid
8700  *packet << aItem->GetCount(); // stacksize
8701  *packet << uint32((min < max) ? min : max); // starting bid
8702  *packet << uint32((max > min) ? max : min); // buyout
8703  *packet << uint32(etime); // auction duration
8704 
8705  m_bot->GetSession()->QueuePacket(std::move(packet)); // queue the packet to get around race condition
8706  }
8707 }
8708 
8709 void PlayerbotAI::Buy(Creature* vendor, const uint32 itemid)
8710 {
8711  if (!vendor)
8712  return;
8713 
8714  // DEBUG_LOG("vendor (%s) itemid (%u)",vendor->GetName(),itemid);
8715 
8716  VendorItemData const* vItems = vendor->GetVendorItems();
8717  VendorItemData const* tItems = vendor->GetVendorTemplateItems();
8718 
8719  uint8 customitems = vItems ? vItems->GetItemCount() : 0;
8720  uint8 numitems = customitems + (tItems ? tItems->GetItemCount() : 0);
8721 
8722  for (uint8 vendorslot = 0; vendorslot < numitems; ++vendorslot)
8723  {
8724  VendorItem const* crItem = vendorslot < customitems ? vItems->GetItem(vendorslot) : tItems->GetItem(vendorslot - customitems);
8725 
8726  if (crItem)
8727  {
8728  if (itemid != crItem->item)
8729  continue;
8730 
8731  ItemPrototype const* pProto = ObjectMgr::GetItemPrototype(itemid);
8732  if (pProto)
8733  {
8734  // class wrong item skip only for bindable case
8735  if ((pProto->AllowableClass & m_bot->getClassMask()) == 0 && pProto->Bonding == BIND_WHEN_PICKED_UP)
8736  continue;
8737 
8738  // race wrong item skip always
8739  if ((pProto->Flags2 & ITEM_FLAG2_FACTION_HORDE) && m_bot->GetTeam() != HORDE)
8740  continue;
8741 
8742  if ((pProto->Flags2 & ITEM_FLAG2_FACTION_ALLIANCE) && m_bot->GetTeam() != ALLIANCE)
8743  continue;
8744 
8745  if ((pProto->AllowableRace & m_bot->getRaceMask()) == 0)
8746  continue;
8747 
8748  // possible item coverting for BoA case
8749  if (pProto->Flags & ITEM_FLAG_IS_BOUND_TO_ACCOUNT)
8750  // convert if can use and then buy
8751  if (pProto->RequiredReputationFaction && uint32(m_bot->GetReputationRank(pProto->RequiredReputationFaction)) >= pProto->RequiredReputationRank)
8752  // checked at convert data loading as existed
8753  if (uint32 newItemId = sObjectMgr.GetItemConvert(itemid, m_bot->getRaceMask()))
8754  pProto = ObjectMgr::GetItemPrototype(newItemId);
8755  m_bot->BuyItemFromVendorSlot(vendor->GetObjectGuid(), vendorslot, itemid, 1, NULL_BAG, NULL_SLOT);
8756  return;
8757  }
8758  }
8759  }
8760 }
8761 
8762 void PlayerbotAI::Sell(const uint32 itemid)
8763 {
8764  Item* pItem = FindItem(itemid);
8765  if (pItem)
8766  {
8767  std::ostringstream report;
8768 
8769  ItemPrototype const* pProto = pItem->GetProto();
8770 
8771  if (!pProto)
8772  return;
8773 
8774  uint32 cost = pItem->GetProto()->SellPrice * pItem->GetCount();
8775 
8776  // handle spell charge if any
8777  for (auto i = 0; i < MAX_ITEM_PROTO_SPELLS; ++i)
8778  {
8779  auto const& spell = pProto->Spells[i];
8780 
8781  // if spell charges for this item are negative, it means that the item should be destroyed once the charges are consumed.
8782  // it also means that the value of this item is relative to how many charges are remaining.
8783  if (spell.SpellId != 0 && spell.SpellCharges < 0)
8784  {
8785  auto const multiplier = static_cast<float>(pItem->GetSpellCharges(i)) / spell.SpellCharges;
8786  cost *= multiplier;
8787  break;
8788  }
8789  }
8790 
8791  m_bot->MoveItemFromInventory(pItem->GetBagSlot(), pItem->GetSlot(), true);
8792  m_bot->AddItemToBuyBackSlot(pItem, cost);
8793  m_bot->ModifyMoney(cost);
8794 
8795  report << "Sold ";
8796  MakeItemLink(pItem, report, true);
8797  report << " for " << Cash(cost);
8798 
8799  TellMaster(report.str());
8800  }
8801 }
8802 
8803 void PlayerbotAI::SellGarbage(Player& /*player*/, bool bListNonTrash, bool bDetailTrashSold, bool bVerbose)
8804 {
8805  uint32 SoldCost = 0;
8806  uint32 SoldQuantity = 0;
8807  bool sellableItems = false;
8808  std::ostringstream report, goods;
8809 
8810  // list out items in main backpack
8811  for (uint8 slot = INVENTORY_SLOT_ITEM_START; slot < INVENTORY_SLOT_ITEM_END; ++slot)
8812  {
8813  Item* const item = m_bot->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, slot);
8814  if (item)
8815  _doSellItem(item, report, goods, SoldCost, SoldQuantity);
8816  }
8817  if (goods.str().size() > 0)
8818  sellableItems = true;
8819  if (bVerbose && bListNonTrash && goods.str().size() > 0) // Tell master of unsold items
8820  TellMaster("Unsold items in my main backpack: %s", goods.str().c_str());
8821 
8822  // and each of our other packs
8823  for (uint8 bag = INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_START; bag < INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_END; ++bag) // check for extra bags
8824  {
8825  std::ostringstream subBagGoods;
8826  const Bag* const pBag = static_cast<Bag*>(m_bot->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, bag));
8827  if (pBag)
8828  {
8829  for (uint8 slot = 0; slot < pBag->GetBagSize(); ++slot)
8830  {
8831  Item* const item = m_bot->GetItemByPos(bag, slot);
8832  if (item)
8833  _doSellItem(item, report, subBagGoods, SoldCost, SoldQuantity);
8834  }
8835  if (subBagGoods.str().size() > 0)
8836  sellableItems = true;
8837  if (bVerbose && bListNonTrash && subBagGoods.str().size() > 0) // Tell master of unsold items
8838  {
8839  const ItemPrototype* const bagProto = pBag->GetProto(); // Get bag name to help master retrieve it
8840  std::string bagName = bagProto->Name1;
8841  ItemLocalization(bagName, bagProto->ItemId);
8842  TellMaster("Unsold items in my %s: %s", bagName.c_str(), subBagGoods.str().c_str());
8843  }
8844  }
8845  }
8846 
8847  if (!bDetailTrashSold) // no trash got sold
8848  report.str(""); // clear ostringstream
8849 
8850  if (SoldCost > 0)
8851  {
8852  if (bDetailTrashSold)
8853  report << "Sold total " << SoldQuantity << " item(s) for ";
8854  else
8855  report << "Sold " << SoldQuantity << " trash item(s) for ";
8856  report << Cash(SoldCost);
8857 
8858  if (bVerbose)
8859  TellMaster(report.str());
8860  }
8861 
8862  // For all bags, non-gray sellable items
8863  if (bVerbose)
8864  {
8865  if (SoldQuantity == 0 && !sellableItems)
8866  TellMaster("No items to sell, trash or otherwise.");
8867  }
8868 }

8870 // no time to sell junk, then just drop it...
8871 bool PlayerbotAI::DropGarbage(bool bVerbose)
8872 {
8873  std::ostringstream report;
8874  bool autodrop = false, junk = false;
8875 
8876  if (bVerbose)
8877  report << "Dropping ";
8878 
8879  // list out items in main backpack
8880  for (uint8 slot = INVENTORY_SLOT_ITEM_START; slot < INVENTORY_SLOT_ITEM_END; ++slot)
8881  {
8882  autodrop = false;
8883  Item* const item = m_bot->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, slot);
8884  if (item)
8885  {
8886  ItemPrototype const* pProto = item->GetProto();
8887  if (item->CanBeTraded() && item->GetProto()->Quality == ITEM_QUALITY_POOR) // trash sells automatically.
8888  {
8889  junk = true;
8890  report << DropItem(pProto->ItemId);
8891  }
8892  if (m_dropWhite && item->GetProto()->SellPrice > 0 && (item->GetProto()->Quality == ITEM_QUALITY_NORMAL || item->GetProto()->Quality == ITEM_QUALITY_UNCOMMON) && item->GetProto()->SubClass != ITEM_SUBCLASS_QUEST)
8893  {
8894  if (pProto->RequiredLevel < (m_bot->GetLevel() - m_mgr.gConfigSellLevelDiff) && pProto->SubClass != ITEM_SUBCLASS_WEAPON_MISC && pProto->FoodType == 0)
8895  {
8896  if (pProto->Class == ITEM_CLASS_WEAPON)
8897  autodrop = true;
8898  if (pProto->Class == ITEM_CLASS_ARMOR)
8899  autodrop = true;
8900  }
8901  if (pProto->SubClass == ITEM_SUBCLASS_FOOD && (pProto->RequiredLevel < (m_bot->GetLevel() - m_mgr.gConfigSellLevelDiff)))
8902  {
8903  autodrop = true;
8904  }
8905  if (autodrop)
8906  {
8907  junk = true;
8908  report << DropItem(pProto->ItemId);
8909  }
8910  }
8911  }
8912  }
8913 
8914  // and each of our other packs
8915  for (uint8 bag = INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_START; bag < INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_END; ++bag) // check for extra bags
8916  {
8917  const Bag* const pBag = static_cast<Bag*>(m_bot->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, bag));
8918  if (pBag)
8919  {
8920  for (uint8 slot = 0; slot < pBag->GetBagSize(); ++slot)
8921  {
8922  autodrop = false;
8923  Item* const item = m_bot->GetItemByPos(bag, slot);
8924  if (item)
8925  {
8926  ItemPrototype const* pProto = item->GetProto();
8927  if (item->CanBeTraded() && item->GetProto()->Quality == ITEM_QUALITY_POOR) // trash sells automatically.
8928  {
8929  junk = true;
8930  report << DropItem(pProto->ItemId);
8931  }
8932  if (m_dropWhite && item->GetProto()->SellPrice > 0 && (item->GetProto()->Quality == ITEM_QUALITY_NORMAL || item->GetProto()->Quality == ITEM_QUALITY_UNCOMMON) && item->GetProto()->SubClass != ITEM_SUBCLASS_QUEST)
8933  {
8934  if (pProto->RequiredLevel < (m_bot->GetLevel() - m_mgr.gConfigSellLevelDiff) && pProto->SubClass != ITEM_SUBCLASS_WEAPON_MISC && pProto->FoodType == 0)
8935  {
8936  if (pProto->Class == ITEM_CLASS_WEAPON)
8937  autodrop = true;
8938  if (pProto->Class == ITEM_CLASS_ARMOR)
8939  autodrop = true;
8940  }
8941  if (pProto->SubClass == ITEM_SUBCLASS_FOOD && (pProto->RequiredLevel < (m_bot->GetLevel() - m_mgr.gConfigSellLevelDiff)))
8942  {
8943  autodrop = true;
8944  }
8945  if (autodrop)
8946  {
8947  junk = true;
8948  report << DropItem(pProto->ItemId);
8949  }
8950  }
8951  }
8952  }
8953  }
8954  }
8955  if (bVerbose)
8956  TellMaster(report.str());
8957  return junk;
8958 }

9003 // handle commands sent through chat channels
9004 void PlayerbotAI::HandleCommand(const std::string& text, Player& fromPlayer)
9005 {
9006  // prevent bot task spam
9007  m_inventory_full = false;
9008  m_tasks.unique();
9009  m_findNPC.unique();
9010 
9011  if (m_bDebugCommandChat)
9012  {
9013  DEBUG_LOG("chat(%s)", text.c_str());
9014  TellMaster(text);
9015  }
9016 
9017  // ignore any messages from Addons
9018  if (text.empty() ||
9019  text.find("X-Perl") != std::wstring::npos ||
9020  text.find("HealBot") != std::wstring::npos ||
9021  text.find("HealComm") != std::wstring::npos || // "HealComm 99990094"
9022  text.find("LOOT_OPENED") != std::wstring::npos ||
9023  text.find("CTRA") != std::wstring::npos ||
9024  text.find("GathX") == 0) // Gatherer
9025  return;
9026 
9027  // if message is not from a player in the masters account auto reply and ignore
9028  if (!canObeyCommandFrom(fromPlayer))
9029  {
9030  // only tell the player once instead of endlessly nagging them
9031  if (m_ignorePlayersChat.find(fromPlayer.GetObjectGuid()) == m_ignorePlayersChat.end())
9032  {
9033  std::string msg = "I can't talk to you. Please speak to my master ";
9034  msg += GetMaster()->GetName();
9035  SendWhisper(msg, fromPlayer);
9036  m_bot->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_NO);
9037  m_ignorePlayersChat.insert(fromPlayer.GetObjectGuid());
9038  }
9039  return;
9040  }
9041 
9042  // Passed along to ExtractCommand, if (sub)command is found "input" will only contain the rest of the string (or "")
9043  std::string input = text.c_str();
9044 
9045  // if in the middle of a trade, and player asks for an item/money
9046  // WARNING: This makes it so you can't use any other commands during a trade!
9047  if (m_bot->GetTrader() && m_bot->GetTrader()->GetObjectGuid() == fromPlayer.GetObjectGuid())
9048  {
9049  uint32 copper = extractMoney(text);
9050  if (copper > 0)
9051  TradeCopper(copper);
9052 
9053  std::list<uint32> itemIds;
9054  extractItemIds(text, itemIds);
9055  if (itemIds.size() == 0)
9056  SendWhisper("Show me what item you want by shift clicking the item in the chat window.", fromPlayer);
9057  else if (!strncmp(text.c_str(), "nt ", 3))
9058  {
9059  if (itemIds.size() > 1)
9060  SendWhisper("There is only one 'Will not be traded' slot. Shift-click just one item, please!", fromPlayer);
9061  else
9062  {
9063  std::list<Item*> itemList;
9064  findItemsInEquip(itemIds, itemList);
9065  findItemsInInv(itemIds, itemList);
9066  if (itemList.size() > 0)
9067  TradeItem((**itemList.begin()), TRADE_SLOT_NONTRADED);
9068  else
9069  SendWhisper("I do not have this item equipped or in my bags!", fromPlayer);
9070  }
9071  }
9072  else
9073  {
9074  std::list<Item*> itemList;
9075  findItemsInInv(itemIds, itemList);
9076  for (std::list<Item*>::iterator it = itemList.begin(); it != itemList.end(); ++it)
9077  TradeItem(**it);
9078  }
9079  }
9080 
9081  else if (ExtractCommand("help", input))
9082  _HandleCommandHelp(input, fromPlayer);
9083 
9084  // debug can be enabled without needing to change playerbot.conf file
9085  else if (text == "debug")
9086  {
9087  TellMaster("Debugging is on. Type 'no debug' to disable.");
9088  m_debugWhisper = true;
9089  }
9090  else if (text == "no debug")
9091  {
9092  TellMaster("Debugging is off.");
9093  m_debugWhisper = false;
9094  }
9095 
9096  else if (fromPlayer.GetSession()->GetSecurity() > SEC_PLAYER && ExtractCommand("gm", input))
9097  _HandleCommandGM(input, fromPlayer);
9098 
9099  else if (ExtractCommand("reset", input))
9100  _HandleCommandReset(input, fromPlayer);
9101  else if (ExtractCommand("orders", input))
9102  _HandleCommandOrders(input, fromPlayer);
9103  else if (ExtractCommand("follow", input) || ExtractCommand("come", input))
9104  _HandleCommandFollow(input, fromPlayer);
9105  else if (ExtractCommand("stay", input) || ExtractCommand("stop", input))
9106  _HandleCommandStay(input, fromPlayer);
9107  else if (ExtractCommand("attack", input))
9108  _HandleCommandAttack(input, fromPlayer);
9109  else if (ExtractCommand("pull", input))
9110  _HandleCommandPull(input, fromPlayer);
9111 
9112  else if (ExtractCommand("neutralize", input) || ExtractCommand("neutral", input))
9113  _HandleCommandNeutralize(input, fromPlayer);
9114 
9115  else if (ExtractCommand("cast", input, true)) // true -> "cast" OR "c"
9116  _HandleCommandCast(input, fromPlayer);
9117 
9118  else if (ExtractCommand("sell", input))
9119  _HandleCommandSell(input, fromPlayer);
9120 
9121  else if (ExtractCommand("buy", input))
9122  _HandleCommandBuy(input, fromPlayer);
9123 
9124  else if (ExtractCommand("drop", input))
9125  _HandleCommandDrop(input, fromPlayer);
9126 
9127  else if (ExtractCommand("repair", input))
9128  _HandleCommandRepair(input, fromPlayer);
9129 
9130  else if (ExtractCommand("auction", input))
9131  _HandleCommandAuction(input, fromPlayer);
9132 
9133  else if (ExtractCommand("mail", input))
9134  _HandleCommandMail(input, fromPlayer);
9135 
9136  else if (ExtractCommand("bank", input))
9137  _HandleCommandBank(input, fromPlayer);
9138 
9139  else if (ExtractCommand("talent", input))
9140  _HandleCommandTalent(input, fromPlayer);
9141 
9142  else if (ExtractCommand("use", input, true)) // true -> "use" OR "u"
9143  _HandleCommandUse(input, fromPlayer);
9144 
9145  else if (ExtractCommand("equip", input, true)) // true -> "equip" OR "e"
9146  _HandleCommandEquip(input, fromPlayer);
9147 
9148  // find project: 20:50 02/12/10 rev.4 item in world and wait until ordered to follow
9149  else if (ExtractCommand("find", input, true)) // true -> "find" OR "f"
9150  _HandleCommandFind(input, fromPlayer);
9151 
9152  // get project: 20:50 02/12/10 rev.4 compact edition, handles multiple linked gameobject & improves visuals
9153  else if (ExtractCommand("get", input, true)) // true -> "get" OR "g"
9154  _HandleCommandGet(input, fromPlayer);
9155 
9156  // Handle all collection related commands here
9157  else if (ExtractCommand("collect", input))
9158  _HandleCommandCollect(input, fromPlayer);
9159 
9160  else if (ExtractCommand("quest", input))
9161  _HandleCommandQuest(input, fromPlayer);
9162 
9163  else if (ExtractCommand("craft", input))
9164  _HandleCommandCraft(input, fromPlayer);
9165 
9166  else if (ExtractCommand("enchant", input))
9167  _HandleCommandEnchant(input, fromPlayer);
9168 
9169  else if (ExtractCommand("process", input))
9170  _HandleCommandProcess(input, fromPlayer);
9171 
9172  else if (ExtractCommand("pet", input))
9173  _HandleCommandPet(input, fromPlayer);
9174 
9175  else if (ExtractCommand("spells", input))
9176  _HandleCommandSpells(input, fromPlayer);
9177 
9178  // survey project: 20:50 02/12/10 rev.4 compact edition
9179  else if (ExtractCommand("survey", input))
9180  _HandleCommandSurvey(input, fromPlayer);
9181 
9182  // Handle class & professions training:
9183  else if (ExtractCommand("skill", input))
9184  _HandleCommandSkill(input, fromPlayer);
9185 
9186  // stats project: 11:30 15/12/10 rev.2 display bot statistics
9187  else if (ExtractCommand("stats", input))
9188  _HandleCommandStats(input, fromPlayer);
9189 
9190  else
9191  {
9192  // if this looks like an item link, reward item it completed quest and talking to NPC
9193  std::list<uint32> itemIds;
9194  extractItemIds(text, itemIds);
9195  if (!itemIds.empty())
9196  {
9197  uint32 itemId = itemIds.front();
9198  bool wasRewarded = false;
9199  ObjectGuid questRewarderGUID = m_bot->GetSelectionGuid();
9200  Object* const pNpc = (WorldObject*) m_bot->GetObjectByTypeMask(questRewarderGUID, TYPEMASK_CREATURE_OR_GAMEOBJECT);
9201  if (!pNpc)
9202  return;
9203 
9204  QuestMenu& questMenu = m_bot->GetPlayerMenu()->GetQuestMenu();
9205  for (uint32 iI = 0; !wasRewarded && iI < questMenu.MenuItemCount(); ++iI)
9206  {
9207  QuestMenuItem const& qItem = questMenu.GetItem(iI);
9208 
9209  uint32 questID = qItem.m_qId;
9210  Quest const* pQuest = sObjectMgr.GetQuestTemplate(questID);
9211  QuestStatus status = m_bot->GetQuestStatus(questID);
9212 
9213  // if quest is complete, turn it in
9214  if (status == QUEST_STATUS_COMPLETE &&
9215  !m_bot->GetQuestRewardStatus(questID) &&
9216  pQuest->GetRewChoiceItemsCount() > 1 &&
9217  m_bot->CanRewardQuest(pQuest, false))
9218  for (uint8 rewardIdx = 0; !wasRewarded && rewardIdx < pQuest->GetRewChoiceItemsCount(); ++rewardIdx)
9219  {
9220  ItemPrototype const* const pRewardItem = sObjectMgr.GetItemPrototype(pQuest->RewChoiceItemId[rewardIdx]);
9221  if (itemId == pRewardItem->ItemId)
9222  {
9223  m_bot->RewardQuest(pQuest, rewardIdx, pNpc, false);
9224 
9225  std::string itemName = pRewardItem->Name1;
9226  m_bot->GetPlayerbotAI()->ItemLocalization(itemName, pRewardItem->ItemId);
9227 
9228  std::ostringstream out;
9229  MakeItemLink(pRewardItem, out);
9230  SendWhisper(out.str(), fromPlayer);
9231  wasRewarded = true;
9232  }
9233  }
9234  }
9235  }
9236  else
9237  {
9238  // TODO: make this only in response to direct whispers (chatting in party chat can in fact be between humans)
9239  const std::string msg = "What is '%s'? For a list of commands, ask for 'help'.";
9240  const size_t msglength = (msg.length() - 2);
9241  const size_t limit = (255 - msglength);
9242 
9243  std::string echo = text;
9244  if (echo.length() > limit)
9245  {
9246  utf8limit(echo, (limit - 3));
9247  echo += "...";
9248  }
9249 
9250  const size_t length = (msglength + echo.length());
9251 
9252  std::string reply;
9253  reply.reserve(length);
9254  std::snprintf(reply.data(), reply.capacity(), msg.c_str(), echo.c_str());
9255 
9256  SendWhisper(reply, fromPlayer);
9257  m_bot->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_TALK);
9258  }
9259  }
9260 }
9261 
9271 bool PlayerbotAI::ExtractCommand(const std::string sLookingFor, std::string& text, bool bUseShort)
9272 {
9273  // ("help" + " ") < "help X" AND text's start (as big as sLookingFor) == sLookingFor
9274  // Recommend AGAINST adapting this for non-space situations (thinking MangosZero)
9275  // - unknown would risk being (short for "use") 'u' + "nknown"
9276  if (sLookingFor.size() + 1 < text.size() && text.at(sLookingFor.size()) == ' '
9277  && 0 == text.substr(0, sLookingFor.size()).compare(sLookingFor))
9278  {
9279  text = text.substr(sLookingFor.size() + 1);
9280  return true;
9281  }
9282 
9283  if (0 == text.compare(sLookingFor))
9284  {
9285  text = "";
9286  return true;
9287  }
9288 
9289  if (bUseShort)
9290  {
9291  if (text.size() > 1 && sLookingFor.at(0) == text.at(0) && text.at(1) == ' ')
9292  {
9293  text = text.substr(2);
9294  return true;
9295  }
9296  else if (text.size() == 1 && sLookingFor.at(0) == text.at(0))
9297  {
9298  text = "";
9299  return true;
9300  }
9301  }
9302 
9303  return false;
9304 }

9324 void PlayerbotAI::_HandleCommandOrders(std::string& text, Player& fromPlayer)
9325 {
9326  if (ExtractCommand("delay", text))
9327  {
9328  uint32 gdelay;
9329  sscanf(text.c_str(), "%d", &gdelay);
9330  if (gdelay <= 10)
9331  {
9332  m_DelayAttack = gdelay;
9333  TellMaster("Combat delay is now '%u' ", m_DelayAttack);
9334  CharacterDatabase.DirectPExecute("UPDATE playerbot_saved_data SET combat_delay = '%u' WHERE guid = '%u'", m_DelayAttack, m_bot->GetGUIDLow());
9335  return;
9336  }
9337  else
9338  SendWhisper("Invalid delay. choose a number between 0 and 10", fromPlayer);
9339  return;
9340  }
9341  else if (ExtractCommand("resume", text))
9342  CombatOrderRestore();
9343  else if (ExtractCommand("combat", text, true))
9344  {
9345  Unit* target = nullptr;
9346 
9347  if (text.empty())
9348  {
9349  SendWhisper("|cffff0000Syntax error:|cffffffff orders combat <botName> <reset | tank | heal | passive><assist | protect [targetPlayer]>", fromPlayer);
9350  return;
9351  }
9352 
9353  QueryResult* resultlvl = CharacterDatabase.PQuery("SELECT guid FROM playerbot_saved_data WHERE guid = '%u'", m_bot->GetObjectGuid().GetCounter());
9354  if (!resultlvl)
9355  CharacterDatabase.DirectPExecute("INSERT INTO playerbot_saved_data (guid,combat_order,primary_target,secondary_target,pname,sname,combat_delay,auto_follow,autoequip) VALUES ('%u',0,0,0,'','',0,0,false)", m_bot->GetObjectGuid().GetCounter());
9356  else
9357  delete resultlvl;
9358 
9359  size_t protect = text.find("protect");
9360  size_t assist = text.find("assist");
9361 
9362  if (ExtractCommand("protect", text) || ExtractCommand("assist", text))
9363  {
9364  ObjectGuid targetGUID = fromPlayer.GetSelectionGuid();
9365  if (text == "" && !targetGUID)
9366  return SendWhisper("|cffff0000Combat orders protect and assist expect a target either by selection or by giving target player in command string!", fromPlayer);
9367 
9368  if (!text.empty())
9369  {
9370  ObjectGuid targ_guid = sObjectMgr.GetPlayerGuidByName(text.c_str());
9371  targetGUID.Set(targ_guid.GetRawValue());
9372  }
9373  target = ObjectAccessor::GetUnit(fromPlayer, targetGUID);
9374  if (!target)
9375  return SendWhisper("|cffff0000Invalid target for combat order protect or assist!", fromPlayer);
9376 
9377  if (protect != std::string::npos)
9378  SetCombatOrder(ORDERS_PROTECT, target);
9379  else if (assist != std::string::npos)
9380  SetCombatOrder(ORDERS_ASSIST, target);
9381  }
9382  else
9383  SetCombatOrderByStr(text, target);
9384  }
9385  else if (!text.empty())
9386  {
9387  SendWhisper("See help for details on using 'orders'.", fromPlayer);
9388  return;
9389  }
9390  SendOrders(*GetMaster());
9391 }

9393 void PlayerbotAI::_HandleCommandFollow(std::string& text, Player& fromPlayer)
9394 {
9395  if (ExtractCommand("auto", text)) // switch to automatic follow distance
9396  {
9397  if (!text.empty())
9398  {
9399  SendWhisper("Invalid subcommand for 'follow'", fromPlayer);
9400  return;
9401  }
9402  DistOverRide = 0; // this resets follow distance to config default
9403  IsUpOrDown = 0;
9404  std::ostringstream msg;
9405  gTempDist = 1;
9406  gTempDist2 = 2;
9407 
9408  if (m_FollowAutoGo != FOLLOWAUTOGO_SET)
9409  {
9410  m_FollowAutoGo = FOLLOWAUTOGO_INIT;
9411  msg << "Automatic Follow Distance is now |h|cff1eff00ON|h|r";
9412  SendWhisper(msg.str(), fromPlayer);
9413  }
9414  else
9415  {
9416  m_FollowAutoGo = FOLLOWAUTOGO_OFF;
9417  msg << "Automatic Follow Distance is now |h|cffff0000OFF|h|r";
9418  SendWhisper(msg.str(), fromPlayer);
9419  }
9420  CharacterDatabase.DirectPExecute("UPDATE playerbot_saved_data SET auto_follow = '%u' WHERE guid = '%u'", m_FollowAutoGo, m_bot->GetGUIDLow());
9421  }
9422  else if (ExtractCommand("reset", text)) // switch to reset follow distance
9423  {
9424  if (!text.empty())
9425  {
9426  SendWhisper("Invalid subcommand for 'follow'", fromPlayer);
9427  return;
9428  }
9429  DistOverRide = 0; // this resets follow distance to config default
9430  IsUpOrDown = 0;
9431  std::ostringstream msg;
9432  gTempDist = 1;
9433  gTempDist2 = 2;
9434  msg << "Bit crowded isn't it?";
9435  SendWhisper(msg.str(), fromPlayer);
9436  }
9437  else if (ExtractCommand("far", text)) // switch to increment follow distance
9438  {
9439  if (!text.empty())
9440  {
9441  SendWhisper("Invalid subcommand for 'follow'", fromPlayer);
9442  return;
9443  }
9444  DistOverRide = (DistOverRide + 1); // this increments follow distance
9445  std::ostringstream msg;
9446  msg << "Increasing My follow distance";
9447  SendWhisper(msg.str(), fromPlayer);
9448  }
9449  else if (ExtractCommand("near", text)) // switch to increment follow distance
9450  {
9451  if (!text.empty())
9452  {
9453  SendWhisper("Invalid subcommand for 'follow'", fromPlayer);
9454  return;
9455  }
9456  if (DistOverRide > 0)
9457  DistOverRide = (DistOverRide - 1); // this increments follow distance,
9458 
9459  std::ostringstream msg;
9460  if (DistOverRide == 0)
9461  {
9462  IsUpOrDown = 0;
9463  DistOverRide = 0;
9464  gTempDist = 1;
9465  gTempDist2 = 2;
9466  msg << "I'm NOT getting any closer than this";
9467  }
9468  if (DistOverRide != 0)
9469  msg << "Decreasing My follow distance";
9470  SendWhisper(msg.str(), fromPlayer);
9471  }
9472  else if (ExtractCommand("info", text))
9473  {
9474  std::ostringstream msg;
9475 
9476  msg << "Automatic Follow Distance is ";
9477 
9478  switch (DistOverRide)
9479  {
9480  case 0: msg << "|h|cffff0000" << m_bot->GetDistance(GetMaster()) << "|h|r"; break; //red
9481  case 1: msg << "|h|cffff8000" << m_bot->GetDistance(GetMaster()) << "|h|r"; break; //yellow
9482  case 2: msg << "|h|cffe6cc80" << m_bot->GetDistance(GetMaster()) << "|h|r"; break; //orange
9483  case 3: msg << "|h|cff1eff00" << m_bot->GetDistance(GetMaster()) << "|h|r"; break; //green
9484  case 4:
9485  default: msg << "|h|cff0070dd" << m_bot->GetDistance(GetMaster()) << "|h|r"; break; //blue
9486  }
9487 
9488  m_FollowAutoGo ? SendWhisper(msg.str(), fromPlayer) : SendWhisper("Automatic Follow Distance is |h|cffff0000OFF|h|r", fromPlayer);
9489  return;
9490  }
9491  else if (!text.empty())
9492  {
9493  SendWhisper("see help for details on using follow.", fromPlayer);
9494  return;
9495  }
9496  SetMovementOrder(MOVEMENT_FOLLOW, GetMaster());
9497 }

9509 void PlayerbotAI::_HandleCommandAttack(std::string& text, Player& fromPlayer)
9510 {

9512  {
9513  SendWhisper("attack cannot have a subcommand.", fromPlayer);
9514  return;
9515  }

9517  if (attackOnGuid)
9518  {

9526  Attack(thingToAttack);
9527  }
9528  }
9529  }
9530  else
9531  {
9532  SendWhisper("No target is selected.", fromPlayer);
9533  m_bot->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_TALK);
